summary: "Mia Khalifa" is a song by iLoveFriday, an American hip hop duo. Released in 2018, it's a diss track aimed at Internet celebrity Mia Khalifa. The song started as a misunderstanding from a fake screenshot. Critics liked its catchiness, but some called it off-key and misogynistic. It became viral on TikTok, especially for the line "Hit or miss, I guess they never miss, huh?"
title: Mia Khalifa (song)
